movies.title: Paper Prince
movies.plot: When seven-year-old Julia's parents go out and leave her at home alone, she opens the door to a suspicious stranger. Six months later, the consequences of this launch Julia and her friends on a breakneck quest to save her family. In the course of this she becomes aware of how the world works and the place she and her family occupy in it.

biography.bio: Milica Spasojevic was born on March 19, 1998 in Belgrade, Serbia. She is an actress, known for Paper Prince (2007), Princ od papira (2005) and Out of the Woods (2017).
biography.name: Milica Spasojevic

biography.bio: Stefan Lazarevic is an actor, known for Paper Prince (2007) and Agi and Emma (2007).
biography.name: Stefan Lazarevic

biography.bio: Milica Mihajlovic was born on June 4, 1972 in Belgrade, Serbia, Yugoslavia. She is an actress, known for Sindjelici (2013), Komsije (2015) and Wait for Me and I Will Not Come (2009). She is married to Vojislav 'Voja' Brajovic.
biography.name: Milica Mihajlovic

biography.bio: Andrej Sepetkovski was born on March 5, 1974 in Aleksinac, Serbia, Yugoslavia. He is an actor, known for Love Comes After (2013), The Mechanism (2000) and The Belgrade Phantom (2009).
biography.name: Andrej Sepetkovski

biography.bio: Goran Radakovic was born on July 11, 1964 in Belgrade, Serbia, Yugoslavia. He is an actor and producer, known for Sindjelici (2013), Three Palms for Two Punks and a Babe (1998) and Strawberries in the Supermarket (2003). He is married to Dubravka Mijatovic.
biography.name: Goran Radakovic

biography.bio: Tatjana Beljakova was born on January 1, 1934 in Mljet, Croatia, Yugoslavia. She is an actress, known for Ratovi (2013), Peta strana sveta (1965) and Tri prání (1958).
biography.name: Tatjana Beljakova

biography.bio: Dragan Petrovic-Pele was born on December 17, 1961 in Belgrade, Serbia, Yugoslavia. He is an actor, known for Joli village, jolie flamme (1996), The Fourth Man (2007) and Absolute Hundred (2001).
biography.name: Dragan Petrovic-Pele

biography.bio: Nada Macankovic was born on August 5, 1982 in Belgrade, Serbia, Yugoslavia. She is an actress, known for Pozoriste u kuci (2007), Ljubav, navika, panika (2005) and The Belgrade Phantom (2009).

biography.bio: Ana Markoski was born on January 25, 1997 in Belgrade, Serbia. She is an actress, known for Paper Prince (2007).

biography.bio: Sonja Savic was born on September 15, 1961 in Cacak, Serbia, Yugoslavia. She was an actress, known for Balkan Spy (1984), Pain et lait (2001) and Gravehopping (2005). She died on September 23, 2008 in Belgrade, Serbia.
biography.name: Sonja Savic

biography.bio: Velimir 'Bata' Zivojinovic was born on June 5, 1933 in Koracica near Mladenovac, Serbia, Yugoslavia. He was an actor, known for Srecni ljudi (1993), Ice (2012) and Joli village, jolie flamme (1996). He was married to Julijana 'Lula' Zivojinovic. He died on May 22, 2016 in Belgrade, Serbia.
biography.name: Velimir 'Bata' Zivojinovic

biography.bio: Marija Perovic is a Montenegrin film director, born on 15th December 1972. in Belgrade, Serbia, Yugoslavia. She graduated on Faculty of Drama Arts Belgrade. She is a director , producer and scriptwriter, known for Packing the Monkeys Again *(Opet pakujemo majmune ) and Look At Me (Gledaj Me). Perovic is a professor of Film and TV directing at Faculty of Drama Arts in Montenegro.
biography.name: Marija Perovic
